  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/vine-for-android-now-runs-on-your-gingerbread-phone/\"><img alt=\"No Vine recording for you, come back one year\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/924f29cb5789b03981b71893edb936f7/vine-android-no-recording.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n手里拿着运行 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/gingerbread\">Gingerbread</a> 的老手机，但也想加入 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/vine\">Vine</a> 的短片社交行列？在最新的 Android 版本中，开发团队算是满足了这些用户的... 部分愿望。据悉在升级后使用 Gingerbread 的用户可以在自己的手机上查看短片，但由于「设备限制」，拍摄功能将无法实现。现在，这样一来会少掉不少乐趣，但还是那句话，有总比没有强吧...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/18/vine-for-android-now-runs-on-your-gingerbread-phone/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://blog.vine.co/post/70430566125/vine-now-available-on-gingerbread-android-devices\" target=\"_blank\">Vine Blog</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=co.vine.android\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/vine-for-android-now-runs-on-your-gingerbread-phone/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20791822/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/19/vine-for-android-now-runs-on-your-gingerbread-phone/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
